</head>
<body>
    <div>
      <div class="container mt-3 loginContainer_2">
          <div class="mt-5" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <button style="order: 1;" id="login-btn" class="login-button">Login</button>
            <h4 style="order: 2; text-align: center; font-size: 40px">Sign up</h4>
            <button style="order: 3;" id="home-btn" class="login-button">Home</button>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-5" style="text-align: center; font-size: 25px">✔️ 비밀번호를 제외한 모든 정보들에 대해서 중복은 불가능합니다 ✔️</h3>
          <form class="mt-5" action="/register" method="POST">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label style="font-size: 30px;">Name (당연히 한국 이름이겠죠?)</label>
                <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control" name="name" placeholder="이름" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-group mt-5">
                <label style="font-size: 30px; display: block;">ID (4~20자 사이의 영문 + 숫자 아이디)</label>
                <div>
                  <input id="registerid" type="text" class="form-control" name="id" placeholder="아이디" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group mt-5">
                <label style="font-size: 30px;">Phone Number (010XXXXXXXX, 하이픈 제외)</label>
                <input id="phone" type="text" class="form-control" name="phonenumber" placeholder="전화번호" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-group mt-5">
                <label style="font-size: 30px;">Password (6~15자, 영문 대소문자, 최소 1개 이상의 숫자 또는 특수문자 포함)</label>
                <input id="pw" type="password" class="form-control" name="pw" placeholder="비밀번호" />
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end;" class="mt-5">
                <button id="signup" type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Sign up</button>
              </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <style>
      .button-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .login-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #ff4d4d;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }
    
      .login-button:hover {
        background-color: #ff6666;
      }
    </style>

